	"packageName": "@fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents-base",
	"readme": [
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "# @fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents-base\n\nBase utilities and types shared across all "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents-*`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " packages.\n\n## Overview\n\nThis library provides the shared infrastructure used by the Angular wrappers for UI5 Web Components. It is installed automatically as a peer dependency of "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents-fiori`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", and "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents-ai`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ".\n\n**What's included:**\n\n- Re-exported UI5 Web Components type enums ("
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`ValueState`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`CalendarType`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`AnimationMode`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", etc.)\n- "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`UI5WrapperCustomEvent<T, N>`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " — TypeScript helper for typed custom event payloads from wrapper components\n- Theming API ("
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`provideUi5Theming`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`Ui5ThemingProvider`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ") for SAP theming integration\n- Language bridge ("
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`provideUi5LanguageBridge`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ") — syncs Fundamental NGX locale to UI5 Web Components\n\n## Installation\n\nThis package is installed automatically as a dependency of the UI5 wrapper libraries:\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```bash\nnpm install @fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\nIf you need it standalone:\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```bash\nnpm install @fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents-base\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\n## Usage\n\n### Typed custom events\n\nUse "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`UI5WrapperCustomEvent<T, N>`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " to get the strongly-typed payload of a UI5 wrapper output:\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```typescript\nimport { UI5WrapperCustomEvent } from '@fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents-base';\nimport { ButtonComponent } from '@fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents';\n\n// Get the event payload type for the \"click\" output of ButtonComponent\ntype ClickEvent = UI5WrapperCustomEvent<ButtonComponent, 'ui5Click'>;\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\n### Re-exported UI5 types\n\nCommon UI5 enums are re-exported so you don't need to import from "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@ui5/webcomponents-base`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " directly:\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```typescript\nimport { ValueState, CalendarType, AnimationMode } from '@fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents-base';\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\n### Language bridge\n\nThe language bridge keeps UI5 Web Components in sync with the Fundamental NGX locale signal. Add it once in your root providers:\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```typescript\n// app.config.ts\nimport { ApplicationConfig } from '@angular/core';\nimport { provideUi5LanguageBridge } from '@fundamental-ngx/ui5-webcomponents-base/i18n';\n\nexport const appConfig: ApplicationConfig = {\n    providers: [provideUi5LanguageBridge()],\n};\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\nAfter this, changing the "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`FD_LANGUAGE_SIGNAL`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " will automatically update the locale used by UI5 Web Components.\n\n## Resources\n\n- [UI5 Web Components Documentation](https://sap.github.io/ui5-webcomponents/)\n- [Fundamental NGX Documentation](https://sap.github.io/fundamental-ngx)\n- [GitHub Repository](https://github.com/SAP/fundamental-ngx)"
		}
	],
